      ul
        li
          a(target='_blank' rel="noopener" href='https://mathmaster13.github.io/') fork by mathmaster13
        li
          a(target='_blank' rel="noopener" href='https://jprogr.github.io/') original site by jProgr
        li
          a(target='_blank' rel="noopener" href='https://aspenlangs.neocities.org/fyn.html') fynotek is a constructed language by mochaspen
